:Section HELP AND ERROR SERVICES
РЇЮ===================================================================================
РЇЮ Special: Provides help info and other special info. 
РЇЮ РѕєF called with this syntax, where РЇ║ stands for the options listed below.
РЇЮ       'РЇ║' РѕєF anything  OR  РѕєFРЇе'РЇ║
РЇЮ Special options (РЇ║).  
РЇЮ  Documented...
РЇЮ    Рѕў РѕЄРЇе'help' | РѕЄРЇе'help-w[ide]'
РЇЮ      Displays the help information in standard (wide) format; returns (1 0РЇ┤0).
РЇЮ    Рѕў РѕЄРЇе'help-n[arrow]'
РЇЮ      Displays the help information in narrow format; returns:  (1 0РЇ┤РЇг).
РЇЮ    Рѕў РѕЄРЇе'parms'
РЇЮ      Resets and returns parameters for ┬Б, `L shortcuts in multi-line form.
РЇЮ    Рѕў РѕЄРЇе'parms-c'
РЇЮ      Resets parameters and returns active parameters for ┬Б, `L options in compact form.
РЇЮ  Undocumented...
РЇЮ    Рѕў РѕЄРЇе'globals'
РЇЮ      Returns all the std global variables with their values.
РЇЮ    * РѕЄРЇе'path'
РЇЮ      Returns all the files and workspace directories used for ┬Б, `L shortcuts.
РЇЮ    * 'get' РѕЄ 'parameter' value
РЇЮ      Returns the current value of the named parameter. The parameter must be valid.
РЇЮ    * 'set' РѕЄ 'parameter'  new_value
РЇЮ      Sets the named parameter to a new value.
РЇЮ      Returns the previous value. The parameter must be valid.
РЇЮ 
  SpecialРєљ { 
    valРєљ РјЋC РЇЋРЇх                                    РЇЮ РЇ║ is referenced for 'get' and 'set' only
  РЇЮ p├бrms: Load any new p├бrms without a ]load. 
  РЇЮ        Returns display of default and user p├бrms (as mx) in alph order.
    2РЅа РјЋNC 'val': РјЋSIGNAL ├фOpt  
  РЇЮ LoadParms (isVerbose isCompact isRuntime)   
    'parms-c'РЅА   val: _Рєљ libUtils.LoadParms  (verbose: 1 РІё compact: 1 РІё runtime: 1)
    'parms'  РЅА 5РєЉval: _Рєљ libUtils.LoadParms  (verbose: 1 РІё compact: 0 РІё runtime: 1) 
    'path'   РЅА   val: _Рєљ libUtils.ShowPath РЇг 
  РЇЮ  globals
    'glo'    РЅА 3РєЉval: _Рєљ ShowGlobalsIf 1                 РЇЮ list all "globals"
  РЇЮ  symbols 
    'sym'    РЅА 3РєЉval: _Рєљ ShowSymbols РЇг                   РЇЮ special symbols
  РЇЮ  * = all of the above
    '*'      РЅА   val: _Рєљ ShowAllРЇг
  РЇЮ If pfx of <val> not 'help', option error.
    'help'   РЅб 4РєЉval: РјЋSIGNAL ├фOpt 
  РЇЮ help | help-n[arrow] | help-w[ide] 
      CLoadHtmlРєљ {   РЇЮ Conditionally load help html file, i.e. if not already loaded...
        22:: РјЋSIGNAL ├фHelpFi 
        0= РјЋNC РЇх: РібРјЋTHIS.helpHtmlРєљ РіЃРјЋNGET HELP_HTML_FI 
          РјЋTHIS.helpHtml  
      }
      RenderHtmlРєљ {  РЇЮ Fallback to Ride, if no HTMLRenderer...
        0::  16 РјЋSIGNALРЇе 'NONCE ERROR: No renderer available to display HELP information'
        0::  РЇгРіБ 3500РїХ РЇ║ 
          РЇгРіБ 'htmlObj' РјЋWC 'HTMLRenderer',РЇЦРіє РЇх 
      }  
      htmlРєљ CLoadHtml 'helpHtml' 
    РЇЮ Screen widths determined by help subtype (wide or narrow).
    РЇЮ Is val 'help-n[arrow]' or 'help[-wide]' (wide is default). 
      sРєљ (900 1000) (900 1350)РіЃРЇе ~'-n'(1РѕўРѕіРЇи)val   
      objРєљ ('HTML' html) (s,РЇе Ріѓ'Size') (15 35,РЇе Ріѓ'Posn') ('Coord' 'ScaledPixel')   
      1 0РЇ┤РЇгРіБ html RenderHtml obj    
  }  
  ShowSymbolsРєљ {
    РєЉ(
      ('  Special: "РЇ╣┬Б`"       РЇЮ РЇ╣:omega-underscore, ┬Б:libra(ry), `:escape') 
      ('  Futures: "', FUTURES,'"')
    )
  } 
  ShowAllРєљ{
      РјЋРєљ 'Symbols:'
      РјЋРєљ ShowSymbolsРЇг
      РјЋРєљ 'Globals:'
      РјЋРєљ ShowGlobalsIf 1
      РјЋРєљ '(Library) Parms:'
      РјЋРєљ '  ',,libUtils.LoadParms  (verbose: 1 РІё compact: 1 РІё runtime: 1)
      РјЋРєљ '(Library) Path:'
      РјЋРєљ '  ',libUtils.ShowPath РЇг
    1: _РєљРЇг
  }      
  
:EndSection HELP AND ERROR SERVICES

