РЇЮ Utilities for "userLibrary" shortcut (┬Б, `L) 
РЇЮ See LoadLibAuto 
:Namespace libUtils
РЇЮРЇЮРЇЮРЇЮРЇЮ This is a local stub, pending (optional, but expected) load of LibUtils below.
  РѕЄ {libNs}Рєљ  LibSimple libNs 
    ; РЇЎreadParms; auto
    РЇЮ external in the stub... 
